@646  = ~Not really. Some remain buried, usually with the dead.~
@647  = ~Yes, I suppose so.~
@648  = ~What are you trying to tell me?~
@649  = ~Other people's secrets don't concern me. I'm incurious.~
@650  = ~Well, you think on it then.~
