@654  = ~We're on our own, and that's how I like it.~
@655  = ~Hmm, maybe you are right. We'll discuss the content of the message later today. ~
@656  = ~I know enough of artists to not begrudge you thinking of your craft first and foremost, but I was not thinking of entertainment, <CHARNAME>.~
